RootViewController with iAds and AdMob support for Cocos2d

Usage:

Replace the RootViewController in the Cocos2d project with the AdRootViewController.

To add the ad to the controller's view call [viewController addBannerAd];

To remove the ad call [viewController removeBannerAd];

You can set the position of the ad at the Top or Bottom of the Screen, just call [viewController setAdBannerPosition:kAdBannerPositionBottom] or [viewController setAdBannerPosition:kAdBannerPositionTop]

The controller rotates the ad automatically using CCDirector autorotation or UIViewController's.

Hope it helps, suggestions and corrections are always welcome.